## Usage

### Automatic Application

Custom instructions and rules are automatically applied by GitHub Copilot based on file type patterns. Copilot reads:
- `.github/copilot-instructions.md` — always applied
- `.claude/rules/*.md` — applied based on `paths:` globs
- `.github/instructions/*.instructions.md` — applied based on `applyTo:` patterns
- `CLAUDE.md` — always applied

### Agent Invocation

Use `@AgentName` in VS Code Copilot chat:

```
@DxCodeReview                           — review current branch
@DxPRReview https://...pullrequest/123  — review a specific PR
@DxTicket 2416553                       — research an ADO ticket
@DxComponent hero                       — find all files for a component
@DxHelp how does authentication work?   — ask about the project
```

